name: Global X Short-Term U.S. Treasury Premium Yield ETF
longDescription: The Fund will generally invest, directly or indirectly, in a portfolio of U.S. Treasury securities denominated in U.S. dollars. The Manager will generally endeavor to maintain a target duration of less than three years for SPAY.U, within a certain band, by employing rules-based security selection methodology and weighting. The ETF seeks to provide exposure to the performance of a portfolio of U.S. Treasury securities.
